    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_AddCrystalReportTemplate",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to manage the addition of Crystal Report templates into a database. It checks if a report template already exists based on its path. If it does, it retrieves the existing template ID. If not, it inserts a new record into two tables: "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Scheduler.ReportTemplate",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " and "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Scheduler.CrystalReportTemplate",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", and returns the new template ID. The procedure uses transactions to ensure data integrity and handles errors by rolling back changes if any issues occur during the insert operations."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Medium"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves conditional logic, transaction management, error handling, and interaction with multiple tables. While the logic is straightforward, the use of transactions and error handling adds a layer of complexity."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
